# Caro

# Description

A gomoku-like game with addtional rules: A player can only win if: - He/she has exactly 5 continuous pieces (no more or less) - These pieces have at least a head or tail not being blocked by the opponent's piece.

There are 2 modes: 1 player (vs AI) and 2 players

